{"word":"ἔσπον","slug":"ἔσπον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42943\" key=\"e)/spon\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἔσπον</orth>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 2</tns> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐνέπω</foreign>: only in <per opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"per\">2</per> <number opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"number\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pl.\">pl.</a></number> in the formula <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔσπετε νῦν μοι, Μοῦσαι</foreign> <sense id=\"n42943.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tell</tr_> me now, ye Muses, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:484\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.484</biblScope></bibl>, al.; later <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔσπετε νῦν μοι ὅσοι πολυπράγμονές ἐστε σοφισταί</foreign> Timo <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>. (Prob. fr. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔν-σπ-ετε</foreign> (<abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l. in</abbr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> </bibl> l. c.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σπ-</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐνι-σπ-εῖν</foreign>) is the weak form of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">seq[uglide],</tr_> cf. Lith. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sekù</tr_> 'say', Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in-sece.</tr_>)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}